      • addAll

        void addAll(Composite c,
            boolean excludeDuplicates)
        Add all the objects of the specified composite to this set. If excludeDuplicates is true then any elements of c which are already contained within this are skipped. Otherwise we attempt to add all elements with the resulting DuplicateChildException if there are any duplicates
